<?xml version="1.0"?>
<strings>
	<!-- English -->
	
	<tag id="ID_TEST">Hi [name], this is a test string from room011 - interrogation room. </tag>
	
		<!-- FAN0  -->
		
	<tag id="ID_FAN0A"><![CDATA[You again?  What do you want now?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_FAN0B"><![CDATA[Yeah, that police officer showed me all the evidence you collected.  We worked out a plea bargain, so there's no point to denying it - I killed her.]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_FAN0C"><![CDATA[I really wanted to meet her that night after the concert.  And after I saw her fighting with her "boyfriend," I thought maybe ... well ... but then it all went wrong!]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_FAN0D"><![CDATA[After she and her boy-toy split, I thought "This is my chance!"  I said I'd be her boyfriend, that I'd treat her right and make her happy!  But she insulted me!  The things she called me!  But ... things got a little out of hand ...]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_FAN0E"><![CDATA[To hide the evidence!  I thought if you couldn't identify her, you'd never get me.]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_FAN0F"><![CDATA[I don't know ... I panicked.  I just wanted her to shut up ... she hit me with her purse, then I had my knife ... then there was blood everywhere, and I knew I had to hide her ...]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_FAN0G"><![CDATA[Since they fought that night, I thought her boyfriend would make a great suspect.  And if he had the murder weapon, well ... maybe you'd arrest him and never find out about me.]]></tag>
	
		<!-- REPLIES TO FAN -->

	<tag id="ID_USER0A"><![CDATA[I know that you killed Freebird Reynolds.]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_USER0B"><![CDATA[When did you kill Freebird?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_USER0C"><![CDATA[Why did you kill Freebird?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_USER0D"><![CDATA[Why did you burn the body?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_USER0E"><![CDATA[What happened?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_USER0F"><![CDATA[What did you do with the knife?]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_USER0EXIT"><![CDATA[I'm done here.]]></tag>

		<!-- END SCREEN -->

	<tag id="ID_NEWSPAPER_NAME"><![CDATA[The Vegas Chronicle]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_NEWSPAPER_HEADLINE"><![CDATA[CSI Solves Starlet Slaughter]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_CONGRATS"><![CDATA[CONGRATULATIONS!]]></tag>
	<tag id="ID_CONGRATS_DETAILS"><![CDATA[You've solved the case.<br><br>]]></tag>
